+Let me also check the event types and inventory repository:Now I understand all the bugs. Let me fix them:Let me check the tests to understand the expected behavior:Let me check the event bus:Found the bug - EventBus uses module-level global handlers that accumulate across test runs. Let me fix this and the other remaining bugs:All 34 tests pass. Fixed 6 bugs:
